        <h1 class="font-18">You get the lowest possible rate - we guarantee it</h1>
        <p>Your booking backed by Gozo's Best Price Guarantee.<br/>
            We are always checking the market for better prices for a great service comparable to Gozo. If you get a quote for a comparable service at a better price than what we quoted you, we will match it and give you 100 in Gozo coins.</p>
